       title="Accounts" id="E-Mail-Accounts">
    <web-summary>
        Explore how to set up email accounts to send and receive emails using IMAP, POP3, and SMTP protocols. Learn to
        add accounts with generic information, and how some clients display avatars via the BIMI protocol.
    </web-summary>

    <tip>
        <p>
            To receive or send e-mails, you need to set up an e-mail account.
        </p>
        <p>
            E-mails are received via the IMAP or POP3
            protocol and sent via the SMTP protocol.
        </p>
    </tip>

    <chapter title="Add Account" id="module-setup">
