            </li>
            <li>
                Transmit Credentials
                <img alt="email-send.png" src="email-send.png" thumbnail="true"/>
            </li>
        </list>

        <note>
            You can test your e-mail configuration by clicking on the test button.
            <img alt="email-test.png" src="email-test.png"/>
        </note>
    </chapter>

    <tip title="Did you already know?">
        <p>
            Some e-mail clients offer the option of displaying an avatar or profile picture via the <a
                href="https://bimigroup.org/">BIMI
            protocol</a>.
        </p>

        <p>
            This is made possible via a DNS entry and can be created <a href="https://bimigroup.org/bimi-generator/">using
            a
            generator</a>.</p>
    </tip>
